\begin_inset Formula $n>1$
\end_inset

, 若
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

具有
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)-$
\end_inset

连通性, 即
\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{0}(X)=\pi_{1}(X)=...=\pi_{n-1}(X)=0$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Rightarrow$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{n}(X)\cong H_{n}(X,\mathbb{Z})$
\end_inset

